Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,I'm a soldier而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.37,0:00:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.54,0:00:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞過危險的轉角追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.65,0:00:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.45,0:00:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.06,0:00:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.87,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.37,0:00:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.71,0:00:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.31,0:00:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.95,0:01:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.28,0:01:01.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.92,0:01:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佔好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.49,0:01:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.86,0:01:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.39,0:01:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.09,0:01:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.90,0:01:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.23,0:01:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.02,0:01:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天下午
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,茅葺總理前往視察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.36,0:01:42.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九州招慰難民居住區  出島營區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.79,0:01:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是首相宣佈廢除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.43,0:01:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難民對策特別處理法以來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.53,0:01:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次到出島視察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.33,0:01:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於對今後將以何種新態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,面對失去生活基礎的招慰難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.54,0:01:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及是否給予日本國籍等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.44,0:02:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本性的修法措施皆未完備下就逕行實施政策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.31,0:02:06.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕無法避免難民的抗議活動日漸加溫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.61,0:02:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來播報財經相關新聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.55,0:02:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛發表的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.33,0:02:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,#05有動機的人們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.57,0:02:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是從總理視察時收到的花束中發現之信件的影本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.98,0:02:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然監識結果還沒出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.61,0:02:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  應該無法檢驗出指紋之類的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.48,0:02:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暗示要暗殺首相的恐嚇信嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.26,0:02:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼這個字樣是什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.42,0:02:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.03,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還以為你或許會知道些什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.33,0:02:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就眼前所看到的似乎是某組織的固有名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.73,0:03:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實從上次那個中國大使館佔領事件之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比較顯眼的許多恐怖活動當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.11,0:03:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光員警廳掌握到的就有七件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.74,0:03:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在犯罪聲明上記載了跟這個標誌相同的字樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.48,0:03:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除此之外  最新發現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是給南陽報社的恐嚇信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.42,0:03:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及這封暗殺首相的預告狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.42,0:03:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這九件犯罪有什麼關聯性嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.66,0:03:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.93,0:03:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許負責事件的縣警同僚有情報傳遞的失誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.67,0:03:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是犯罪動機和思想背景都有著微妙的差異
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更何況犯罪預告的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.71,0:03:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全都只會讓人認定是單獨犯所為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是事情發展至今發現這個標誌的一致性後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.88,0:03:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們才急忙將這一連串事件指定為跨轄區重點偵辦案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.34,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愉快犯：以欣賞犯罪後社會大眾的反應為樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愉快犯或是模仿犯的可能性呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.42,0:03:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前也很難朝這方面研判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道這個標誌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使在警方也只有極少數的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對媒體也沒發表過任何消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.23,0:04:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果這些都是事實
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.17,0:04:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剩下的只有是否為同一個團體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偽裝成單獨犯同時犯下多起恐怖行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.41,0:04:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我認為這是以某種情報為媒介\N笑面男型恐怖活動的興起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.75,0:04:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.48,0:04:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不希望首相的公務繼續停擺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.55,0:04:25.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理的身體狀況如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.39,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只不過是欺騙媒體的措施
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.82,0:04:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於這次的恐嚇事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.59,0:04:37.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總理希望不對媒體發表任何訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.23,0:04:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因此需要你們出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.83,0:04:43.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,您是說要9課擔任總理的貼身警衛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的第六感很敏銳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.64,0:04:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長官(員警廳的首長)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.71,0:04:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以把恐嚇信的正本給我們嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.71,0:04:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人由我們來找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.15,0:04:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們只要負責總理的安全警衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.95,0:04:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了不被媒體發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.65,0:05:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望你們小心謹慎別做出誇張的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.16,0:05:04.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.43,0:05:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全員到首相官邸集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總歸一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.01,0:05:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要我們當總理的褓母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.68,0:05:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.45,0:05:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長對這個案件怎麼推理的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.39,0:05:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來應該不是跑過來趕流行的模仿犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.13,0:05:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預告狀的內容  簡單說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.86,0:05:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是針對總理決定廢止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.33,0:05:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前政權留下的限時法「難民對策特別處理法」這件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反覆抗議「停止歧視  解放難民」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後認定難民問題沒有進展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.34,0:05:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是對國民的背叛行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.81,0:05:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宣稱要對總理執行死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.48,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的內容根本就支離破碎嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.21,0:06:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光憑這樣就算告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.65,0:06:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這一連串事件是同系列組織干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是無法讓我馬上就想通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.59,0:06:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果拿掉這個標誌的一致性確實毫無共通點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.86,0:06:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然不能完全相信員警廳長官說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.53,0:06:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  既然連續出現標有這個標誌的犯罪聲明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.04,0:06:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們也不得不據此展開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.07,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Stand Alone Complex
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.04,0:06:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,的確跟笑面男事件有點相似啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.05,0:06:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,眼前的目標不在推測事件的內幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.32,0:06:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先全力保護總理的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  在此同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.33,0:06:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要從預告狀和標誌這兩條線索抽絲剝繭找出犯人或犯罪集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.13,0:06:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巴特、齋藤還有帕茲和我一起擔任總理的護衛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.10,0:07:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩和石川、波瑪一起調查預告狀和標誌這兩條線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.48,0:07:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.98,0:07:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然茅葺總理昨天靜養一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.82,0:07:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天仍然精神抖擻地參加臨時內閣會議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.26,0:07:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是在懸而未決的難民政策見不到任何進展的狀況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預算委員會將於數日後召開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.63,0:07:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本首位女性總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像已失去內閣剛組成時的光彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,表情很快就變得憂心忡忡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.97,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對預告狀沒有任何回應嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.84,0:07:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然口頭上說要解放難民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.01,0:07:38.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卻沒有付諸行動過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.08,0:07:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來要貫徹這個理念對你而言似乎負擔太重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.75,0:07:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就用適當的制裁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.22,0:07:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在背後推你一把
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:49.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.66,0:07:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟她的密會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.93,0:07:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一生只有一次機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦起事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕不允許目的未達成就抽身離開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  沒有目的就起事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.84,0:08:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管什麼思想都會輕易失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.18,0:08:11.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遭遇挫折
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.91,0:08:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是有動機的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.95,0:08:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.60,0:08:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就是第八件了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.67,0:08:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事您不必親自動手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被你看到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.21,0:08:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我自己喜歡才做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.81,0:08:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正通過獲取活字情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.78,0:08:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做記憶的補強  以便在緊要關頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.25,0:08:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓最有效的主意能脫口而出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.46,0:08:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.49,0:08:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官房那邊轉來的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生出了奇妙的因數呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然想暗殺首相 真是出現了一個大膽的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.04,0:09:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道是什麼人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.61,0:09:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警方尚未特定犯人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.85,0:09:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.48,0:09:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警衛方面呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.32,0:09:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是公安9課負貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,9課嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.25,0:09:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由那邊出馬的話應該不會有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.39,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真要被暗殺了我們也會很傷腦筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.59,0:09:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好  我們也派個人跟著總理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.46,0:09:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先確認發出這個預告的人長什麼模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.63,0:09:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他快落入9課手裏的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.34,0:09:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就設法接到我們這邊來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.74,0:09:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.45,0:09:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得你心不在焉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.65,0:10:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎  因為我在生理期啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.39,0:10:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼看這段時間的任務?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.16,0:10:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該是針對犯罪的攻擊性組織對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.33,0:10:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算有首相的暗殺預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.30,0:10:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像這樣擺明著被別人操控一點意思也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.47,0:10:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不喜歡這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才問你是不是也這樣覺得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.89,0:10:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過去的難民解放機構中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.86,0:10:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有組織使用過相同的標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.07,0:10:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,何況連這個標誌怎麼念都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少要讓人念得出組織名稱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.14,0:10:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,仇  無限大加上武士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.71,0:11:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像有著什麼思想背景啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定出乎意料地只是使用了既有的題材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.19,0:11:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比如說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.99,0:11:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,例如過去偉人留下來的文學戲劇、電影的名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.63,0:11:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代表在歷史事件中登場的組織或人物的標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.40,0:11:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.84,0:11:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個標誌看來是念成「個別的11人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.25,0:11:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是半世紀前寫成的革命評論集的篇名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.22,0:11:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放到這邊來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.62,0:11:42.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Patrick SylveStre 著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.79,0:11:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「對國家與革命的省思初期革命評論集」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有讀過這本書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.16,0:11:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,革命評論集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時這本評論集應該沒有引起什麼話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一般認為有「第三階級的抬頭」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.64,0:11:58.43,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法國大革命
