Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,納粹的種族滅絕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,《卡斯楚與格瓦拉》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.37,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古巴革命
