Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.45,0:12:10.04,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中國文化大革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,《對原理的回歸》等9篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.12,0:12:12.61,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊斯蘭革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.69,0:12:14.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上作者曾親身遭遇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並挑起他擔任革命指導者夢想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十篇《五月革命》
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.59,0:12:19.86,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1968法國五月革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.93,0:12:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,組成了初期革命評論集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，也有人認為還有包括\N因作者本身不把日本發生的事件視為革命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.83,0:12:27.20,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本5.15事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.27,0:12:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而束之高閣的夢幻般的第11篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.64,0:12:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而有問題的這一篇評論好像就叫作「個別的11人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.91,0:12:40.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是沒有任何曾經出版的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯  即便是這個資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.45,0:12:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最多也不過是一些狂熱份子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.08,0:12:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將自己的說法放到網路上如此而已的情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但有一點不容忽視
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.46,0:12:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些狂熱份子都是狂信的個別主義者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.33,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,個人主義者的聖典嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.77,0:13:00.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個標誌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.60,0:13:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次陸自直升機失控的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.67,0:13:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是搜查過殉職駕駛員的住宅嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.91,0:13:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.71,0:13:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.87,0:13:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在房間裏面看到標有這個標誌的字條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.21,0:13:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且佔據中國大使館的那群人報出來的組織名稱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.62,0:13:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得不就是「個別的11人」嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.09,0:13:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此  這的確很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.73,0:13:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  光憑這些還是無法特定出犯人的身份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.50,0:13:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這一層警方應該也掌握到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛到更深的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.94,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論多小的線索都沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.17,0:13:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把跟特定犯人有關的某種東西給我找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.01,0:13:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.54,0:13:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩你檢查裏面裝的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.89,0:13:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是已覺醒的志士給你的訊息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給我想想其中的意義吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.33,0:14:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們據以鬥爭的聖典「個別的11人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.40,0:14:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那篇文章為什麼偉大呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.10,0:14:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他將515事件跟日本的「能樂」相互比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.94,0:14:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並且論述到事件的本質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.71,0:14:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂「能樂」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.31,0:14:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乃是在戰國武士們輕視一切大眾藝術的情況下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.65,0:14:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一得到認同的表演形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相對於許多藝術的本質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.79,0:14:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過只是「反覆演出既定事物」已然成為假像之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.46,0:14:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有能樂限定自己的公演只表演一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.83,0:14:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們認為蘊藏其中的精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.17,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟現實的行動非常接近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.71,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能以革命指導者的身份走完僅有一次的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.44,0:14:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其人生就會昇華為至高的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.15,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英雄到最後以死亡總結一生功過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並得到永恆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.89,0:15:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是Sylvestre所記載的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「個別的11人」的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就繼續下一條
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.67,0:15:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,荒卷課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.80,0:15:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於明天的行程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請您不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.97,0:15:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們隨行時會小心不讓總理感到心煩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.48,0:15:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.95,0:15:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉為了我的私事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.52,0:15:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,課長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.86,0:15:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.53,0:15:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是混在給總理的信件和包裹裏面送來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.24,0:15:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想您還是不要看比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.41,0:15:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過度的保護會變成歧視女性喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.02,0:16:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本找不到評論的內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.12,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,評論裏面提到的事件是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,1932年5月15日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在國家改造運動的混亂當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,海軍青年軍官和陸軍軍官候補生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及農民有志之士發起的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.54,0:16:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事件的中心人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暗殺了當時的首相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.98,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以此為契機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.94,0:16:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本奔向由軍部掌握主導權的時代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然軍官們的行動只能說是殘忍的恐怖行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.05,0:16:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過後來發生的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.79,0:16:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,象徵了這個事件的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.82,0:16:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首相被暗殺之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然陸軍出身的11名青年軍官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接受了軍法審判
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.40,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是這場審判卻開始出現異樣的發展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.37,0:16:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛滿二十歲的這群被告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.84,0:17:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,基於自己的理念拒絕律師的辯護
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著被判死刑的覺悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邊流淚一邊開始陳述
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.48,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是法官、檢察官這邊的軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.12,0:17:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,記者、旁聽席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都跟他們的心情重疊在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.32,0:17:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己也留下淚來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且在公開審判之前幾乎沒出現過的減刑運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.43,0:17:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在檢察官提出論罪求刑的意見後變成了全民運動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.47,0:17:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到9月19日宣判為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.70,0:17:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到了35萬份請願書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最匪夷所思的是到最後甚至有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.47,0:17:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,送了跟被告相同數目的11根手指給法庭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.95,0:17:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,據說往國粹主義傾斜的輿論達到了最高峰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.95,0:17:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,11名青年軍官發起的首相暗殺事件後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.29,0:17:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國家主義藉由將他們視為英雄而得以擴張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.59,0:17:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這篇評論就是被這些經過吸引的作家留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:18:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怕寫作的時候對事件當事人放入過多的感情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多半是從廢棄的義體上切下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,托古薩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.08,0:18:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,官邸收到了11根斷指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.22,0:18:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去查這東西的出處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.72,0:18:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說11根手指!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.79,0:18:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.93,0:18:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.89,0:18:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也在調查那篇評論的線索時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.73,0:18:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到跟515事件相關而且牽涉到11根手指的情節
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.83,0:18:34.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看樣子這裏面大有文章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.45,0:18:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能趕上真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.32,0:18:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多來這裏修行的大德都十分喜愛這幅畫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.93,0:18:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.81,0:19:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.24,0:19:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐禪比起宗教上的意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.35,0:19:23.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更重要的是將人類的罪業從雜念中解放出來的這層涵義吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用我們的話來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.25,0:19:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許就像是把累積在暫存區上的資料消掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.06,0:19:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者說跟做資料同步的意思類似
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.93,0:19:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼說要是跟坐禪的人連線說不定可以下載到「悟」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.89,0:20:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,周圍沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.92,0:20:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過  這個首相還真是任性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.42,0:20:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被當成暗殺目標的時候還搞什麼坐禪嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再加上又不能進本堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.96,0:20:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出事我可不負責喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她應該很瞭解自己的處境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.67,0:20:19.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種時候更是想來坐禪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以她才會同意私下使用攔截者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.94,0:20:23.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攔截者：intercepter 用電子腦內的視聽覺感知通信設備向外界傳送主視點情報的系統\N曾遭到不正當使用，成為竊聽裝置的一種，也是笑臉男事件的最初突破口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.94,0:20:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很佩服她的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.51,0:20:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是只准少校做資料連線實在有點...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.93,0:21:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正義與我同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.46,0:21:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.58,0:21:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒用的  你已經被包圍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔奇克馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.79,0:22:16.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,經過相當強化的義體人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.97,0:22:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從軍方相關人士開始清查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.04,0:22:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.17,0:22:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有你在  我現在已經...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.47,0:22:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的會嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.18,0:22:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定犯人根本沒有殺人的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.68,0:23:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.82,0:23:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.83,0:23:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.13,0:23:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.73,0:23:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽到一個聲音——醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:37.70,0:23:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字——然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.31,0:23:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我省視自身——醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我——時間已經到了
